374
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:40,230
That would be against Fight God's original purpose
when he founded the school.

375
00:36:40,250 --> 00:36:43,970
Yes. Yes.

376
00:36:43,970 --> 00:36:49,290
Two elders, please go visit Cloud Mist Sect.

377
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:52,860
In the future when everything is clear,

378
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:55,200
and the world is in peace,

379
00:36:55,200 --> 00:37:01,130
you two would be the heroes
and the role models of our school.

380
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:08,210
I wonder you just want to provide some medicine,

381
00:37:08,210 --> 00:37:13,500
and ask the old master of Cloud Mist Sect to be
the leader of this alliance, right?

382
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:17,350
You don't want to provide any soldiers, right?

383
00:37:18,390 --> 00:37:20,250
You're so sneaky.

384
00:37:20,250 --> 00:37:22,080
Mi Tengshan.

385
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:24,210
If I go back to school,

386
00:37:24,210 --> 00:37:27,450
and the kids ask me,

387
00:37:27,450 --> 00:37:31,250
darkness is coming
and why aren't you elders doing anything?

388
00:37:31,250 --> 00:37:34,200
What should I say?
Can I say you are in my way?

389
00:37:34,200 --> 00:37:39,220
Are you the turtle? We are colleagues.
I can't say that about you.

390
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:43,230
Also,

391
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:48,490
if teachers and students offer to seek justice,

392
00:37:48,490 --> 00:37:51,910
and attack Soul Hall,
you can't get in the way of that, right?

393
00:37:51,910 --> 00:37:53,840
Who dares?

394
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:03,100
If any student leaves school without permission,

395
00:38:03,100 --> 00:38:06,130
I will abolish their Fight Qi.

396
00:38:06,130 --> 00:38:08,260
I will not tolerate that!

397
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,680
You...

398
00:38:14,770 --> 00:38:19,930
Elder Tengshan. They can't offer.
They can't volunteer.

399
00:38:19,930 --> 00:38:21,120
I think there must be something wrong with you!

400
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:22,310
Something terribly wrong!

401
00:38:22,310 --> 00:38:25,780
