402
00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:28,470
I don't have any connections.

403
00:38:28,470 --> 00:38:34,750
Some people try so hard to get the students
out of the protection of Fight God's seal.

404
00:38:35,390 --> 00:38:37,870
So the Soul Hall can kill them all?

405
00:38:39,010 --> 00:38:40,820
What do you mean?

406
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:43,140
Say it clearly.

407
00:38:43,140 --> 00:38:44,610
Who has the special purpose?

408
00:38:44,610 --> 00:38:46,430
Your Star Fall Pavillion,

409
00:38:46,430 --> 00:38:50,260
and Cloud Mist Sect have so many great fighters.

410
00:38:50,270 --> 00:38:51,850
You guys don't do anything.

411
00:38:51,850 --> 00:38:54,490
Instead you ask the teachers
and students to go risk their lives.

412
00:38:55,910 --> 00:38:57,990
I think that's your special purpose!

413
00:38:57,990 --> 00:38:59,760
Enough!

414
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:03,600
Fighting like crazy. So inappropriate.

415
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:09,300
You guys can wait.

416
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:13,800
You would be happy when Soul Hall kill you all!

417
00:39:21,410 --> 00:39:23,300
I'm finally back.

418
00:39:23,300 --> 00:39:26,220
I want to sleep. Don't talk to me.

419
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:29,100
Don't sleep yet.
Where have you been all this time?

420
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:31,190
Tell us.

421
00:39:31,190 --> 00:39:33,360
Hao Tian. Stop bothering him.

422
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,980
