423
00:39:34,980 --> 00:39:37,090
They thought we are still brothers.

424
00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:39,130
So many people asked about you.

425
00:39:39,130 --> 00:39:41,360
They asked us and we don't know anything.

426
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,330
Fine.

